  1578→// ─── QZ Tray Integration ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  1579→// QZ Tray is a free desktop app that creates a local WebSocket bridge (wss://localhost:8181).
  1580→// The browser sends ESC/POS commands to QZ Tray, and QZ Tray forwards them directly
  1581→// to the LAN printer via raw TCP — this bypasses the cloud server entirely.
  1582→//
  1583→// Download & install: https://qz.io/download/
  1584→// Works with any ESC/POS thermal printer (Xprinter, Epson TM, Star, etc.)
